Invocation Name: alias me
des:
Need a random name and more? 
Ever wonder what your name and career could have been? 
Look no further!

Alias Me is a novelty app to generate a random first & last name, occupation, and hometown. 

This can be used for fun among friends, to generate characters for your roleplaying games, or just to see what kinds of combinations are generated.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
